Paper: hep-th/9712094

Date: 1997-12-09

Title: The kink Casimir energy in a lattice sine-Gordon model

Authors: J.M. Speight

Comments: 10 pages, 4 postscript figures

Journal-ref: Phys.Rev. D49 (1994) 6914-6919

The Casimir energy of quantum fluctuations about the classical kinkconfiguration is computed numerically for a recently proposed latticesine-Gordon model. This energy depends periodically on the kink position and isfound to be approximately sinusoidal.